==English==

===Noun===
'''Fon'''
# A language of [[Benin]] and [[Togo]], specifically, in the southern regions corresponding to the former kingdom of [[Dahomey]].  Also known as [[Fongbe]] or [[Fɔngbe]], it is part of the [[Gbe]] family of West African languages.

====Translations====
* Fon: [[Fɔngbe]]

